{"tid":196254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生理時鐘倒轉晒 點搞好","createTime":"2017-04-11T07:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T07:43:44.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"396b4c25ccf6d3cd72684048c406c54b76cefbe5","tid":196254,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"keep住1點訓，7點起身<br />\n<br />\n（一早訓，e.g. 11,12點訓 就會訓到第朝12點加頭勁攰）<br />\n<br />\n每日朝早精神最差，個腦lag機咁<br />\n<br />\n晏就好啲，專心到，搞到gag, 同人吹到水<br />\n<br />\n夜晚就好撚亢奮，可以multitasking, 完全唔會攰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣掉番轉個生理模式"},{"pid":"ab0a9945edc786f08c0ff4f9d14b663ffba2dbf2","tid":196254,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"改變唔到 唯有接受"},{"pid":"ec777a28ea5982c02d20c56262ee3f0038ff71a3","tid":196254,"uid":88437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"係咪太大壓力?<br />\n試下做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa38ad9f80e7e90680a59b1f2e5bdb125919b04","tid":196254,"uid":25506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285376cb72e37a21fa3d6ff6a2357f763b88d121","tid":196254,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"一點訓七點起其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0edaadbfc8c7b39228abe4030f41f6b61bb129","tid":196254,"uid":67,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯心理時鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b8bae6c69d7af98529f4244ef170cf561f3018","tid":196254,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一點訓七點起其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\"