0Z","msg":"逼自己就得"},{"pid":"42d75addf44d16b0e3d2c5d69df34ed5125926dd","tid":196254,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"唔夠訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efaffecfb8161a290324b8e68174de43ff8b0ff","tid":196254,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1點瞓7點起有幾倒掉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻學果啲全部都咁㗎啦<br />\n你話晏晝1點瞓夜晚7點起先叫掉轉啦</blockquote><br />\n我表達出錯，唔係想講訓教時間<br />\n<br />\n係精神既時間<br />\n<br />\n我想朝早好撚精神，慢慢變攰，到夜晚就又攰又提唔起勁咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家我case係掉轉"},{"pid":"94cff141a5771d0e7a602bd3fc015c1fb09ba273","tid":196254,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一點訓七點起其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係</blockquote><br />\n有幾正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry 7點訓5點起身<br />\n你覺得你會唔會正常過我?"},{"pid":"3b8ffbf2a50fb265a53f141c5a5925a6d8aab92c","tid":196254,"uid":76524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:59:53.000Z","msg":"我好似仲嚴重<br />\n因為宜家番學最早上堂係12點<br />\n慢慢好似慣左無3-4點就訓唔著<br />\n然後第二朝9點幾10點醒,甚至有時會訓更加耐"},{"pid":"02f365697e056b1bf56fc4fe47016e9e34c23c85","tid":196254,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:46:31.000Z","msg":"我8點鐘要起身返學，夜晚2-3點先訓到"},{"pid":"5e55d599b09fbba9e815a5b3a71f621ff617f2e4","tid":196254,"uid":34577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"我平時返工返 08:30 - 20:10，都成 2、3 點先瞓，由星期一 loop 到星期五。<br />\n到星期六、日基本上連街都唔出，淨係喺屋企瞓返夠皮 (講到底其實係冇人約) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e6f76253c3e6d016837053f5b013e04e6f5f0f","tid":196254,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一點訓七點起其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係</blockquote><br />\n有幾正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry 7點訓5點起身<br />\n你覺得你會唔會正常過我?</blockquote><br />\n咁係你更唔正常姐"},{"pid":"911e1ca824b04b275aa1358a52a2dbda75b6d565","tid":196254,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"移民美國"},{"pid":"7a8c39c4490458b28bab80251d983f3488c65bd9","tid":196254,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1點瞓7點起有幾倒掉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻學果啲全部都咁㗎啦<br />\n你話晏晝1點瞓夜晚7點起先叫掉轉啦</blockquote><br />\n我表達出錯，唔係想講訓教時間<br />\n<br />\n係精神既時間<br />\n<br />\n我想朝早好撚精神，慢慢變攰，到夜晚就又攰又提唔起勁咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家我case係掉轉</blockquote><br />\n成個香港做野讀書班人都係咁架啦<br />\n唔夠瞓朝早唔精神 夜晚先精神"},{"pid":"8817b1a27f51e5eeac09c0566a15403fba10e48d","tid":196254,"uid":9144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"去地球另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fbe331e4a5854a39643d93482294c035c546ac","tid":196254,"uid":88437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪太大壓力?<br />\n試下做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係想掉番轉個生理時鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你依家有無啲咩plan呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}